                        <note rend="inline" type="source">611.3331/154: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Uruguay</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Dawson</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-03-30T17:00:00-05:00">March 30, 1938—5
                                p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>13. Your despatch no. 66, March 17, 1938. Proposed note to Uruguayan
                            Minister of Foreign Affairs approved.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi></signed></closer>
